01:00:12.488 --> 01:00:14.490
Nemam pojma.

01:00:34.718 --> 01:00:36.887
Ustani, Philippe.

01:01:14.925 --> 01:01:16.552
Pristajte ti ko saliveno.

01:01:16.552 --> 01:01:18.929
Zbilja.

01:01:28.897 --> 01:01:33.986
