01:03:34.690 --> 01:03:36.233
Hej Yvonne.

01:03:36.233 --> 01:03:39.027
Ne može me čuti.

01:03:39.236 --> 01:03:41.238
Yvonne, vjeruj mi.

01:03:41.280 --> 01:03:42.906
Ok.

01:03:42.906 --> 01:03:45.200
Bit ćemo doma do 8:30.

01:03:45.409 --> 01:03:48.495
Da, doći ćemo na vrijeme, Yvonne.

